{
  "stem": "1799.4",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 372.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I was just climbing up one of those mounds and kept on walkin'.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I walked to a-- walked to about a mile across fields-- the camp was in the middle of nowhere-- across some fields, and maybe two miles.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I came to a house.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I knocked on the door.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And a woman answered, came to the front door, and realized I, you know, was from some camp.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And she said, [SPEAKING NON-ENGLISH], you know, where do you come from?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I answered her in perfect German.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I said, you know where I came from, because you-- you know that there's a camp there.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It's pretty close to you, and things are pretty bad.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "People are dying there and have died.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I want to take a bath.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I want some clothes.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I need some food.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So she--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And she let me in-- and all in German.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She didn't understand why I spoke German.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I took a bath.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they all sat down with me and had a meal.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they said they had a son that was on the front somewhere in Russia or wherever-- maybe not Russia, maybe it was a prison in Russia-- and that the husband was a-- was a village doctor.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they said, you can sleep over here, and you can stay with us.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You know, we'd had no idea this was going on.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Well, during that night-- and I had clothes on from that son-- during that night, the same lieutenant that had freed me, and the rest of his group, came and took command of the house.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "That became their HQ.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they saw me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he said, how come you're here?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You're not supposed to be here?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You're supposed to be in quarantine.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
